WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.190
I see the sun arising upon Africa today.

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:09.589
I see the fire and the

00:00:09.589 --> 00:00:09.599
glory. I see

00:00:09.599 --> 00:00:12.310
the rays of the sun shining upon the

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:14.709
people. I

00:00:14.719 --> 00:00:17.510
see the African people with their

00:00:17.510 --> 00:00:17.520
faces

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:19.750
looking toward the sun.

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:23.590
In this vision, I

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:26.310
see it is olive

00:00:26.310 --> 00:00:26.320
oil—the

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:28.150
Holy Ghost oil running down their

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:31.029
faces. They are dressed in African

00:00:31.039 --> 00:00:33.590
garb with tribal

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:36.310
beads. There

00:00:36.310 --> 00:00:36.320
is

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:39.590
red on these

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.750
outfits and they have headdresses

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:43.590
on. As they are looking toward the

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.830
sun, I see a new oil running down their

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:47.910
faces,

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:50.790
and there is a glory on

00:00:50.790 --> 00:00:50.800
them.

00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:53.029
There

00:00:53.029 --> 00:00:53.039
is

00:00:53.039 --> 00:00:55.830
nothing around but dirt and

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:59.349
these heights, but as this glory is

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:01.270
falling, oil

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:04.149
is

00:01:04.159 --> 00:01:07.030
saturating them. It

00:01:07.030 --> 00:01:07.040
is

00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:08.710
like whenever you

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:12.550
dump oil, it spreads,

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:15.429
and the glory of the Lord is coming upon

00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:18.230
the African people. I see them

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:21.109
jumping

00:01:21.109 --> 00:01:21.119
and

00:01:21.119 --> 00:01:23.429
putting their chests out,

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:27.990
making a

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.230
noise

00:01:30.230 --> 00:01:30.240
and

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:32.469
popping their chests back. They have

00:01:32.479 --> 00:01:34.550
beads and paint on

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:36.630
them, but there

00:01:36.630 --> 00:01:36.640
is

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:39.109
olive oil coming down on them. He

00:01:39.109 --> 00:01:39.119
has

00:01:39.119 --> 00:01:41.830
not forgotten you today.

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:44.149
Many think,

00:01:44.149 --> 00:01:44.159
'Where

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:46.069
is

00:01:46.079 --> 00:01:48.630
the revival for Africa?

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:51.830
Where is the coming of the

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:55.830
King? Where is the Lord? There has been so

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:58.149
much drought

00:01:58.149 --> 00:01:58.159
here.'I

00:01:58.159 --> 00:02:00.149
see the

00:02:00.159 --> 00:02:04.469
drought, but I hear the sound of an

00:02:04.479 --> 00:02:07.830
abundance of rain, even down to the

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.910
Congo. That is what He just said.

00:02:09.910 --> 00:02:09.920
Amidst

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:13.270
great persecution, you

00:02:13.270 --> 00:02:13.280
are

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:16.150
going to

00:02:16.150 --> 00:02:16.160
see

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:18.630
creative

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:21.110
miracles. This is

00:02:21.110 --> 00:02:21.120
going to be

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:24.869
a wave.

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:28.790
A

00:02:28.800 --> 00:02:32.390
wave will come and pull, and

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:34.070
another wave will come right on the

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:36.949
heels of the creative miracles. You

00:02:36.949 --> 00:02:36.959
are

00:02:36.959 --> 00:02:40.630
about to see a wave of

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:43.350
the glory upon this world. It

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:46.309
will come in waves; it will look like one

00:02:46.309 --> 00:02:46.319
is

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:49.030
receding, but another

00:02:49.040 --> 00:02:52.630
wave will come. In the wave of

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:56.470
this glory, I see body parts.

00:02:56.480 --> 00:03:00.790
The wave comes in and it

00:03:00.790 --> 00:03:00.800
recedes

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:03.190
back, but before it even has time to

00:03:03.190 --> 00:03:03.200
recede

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:05.910
back, another glory wave comes

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:12.309
in. In this wave are eyes, ears,

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:16.390
hands, and feet; body parts from My reserves

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:18.869
are coming unto thee. There will be

00:03:18.879 --> 00:03:21.830
creative miracles flowing in Africa

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:24.229
and

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:26.710
America as you

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:31.750
yield to it. I see a Holy Ghost wave

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:34.550
of glory flowing in South America

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:37.270
and hitting all out in the

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:40.070
bush. You will

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:46.309
see the glory of the Lord, and

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:55.030
I will wash it over the people.

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:01.509
It will look

00:04:01.519 --> 00:04:03.509
like a washing and a

00:04:03.519 --> 00:04:05.910
flow. It will flow

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:29.189
unlike anything you have ever seen before. I

00:04:29.189 --> 00:04:29.199
hear

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:31.990
the Lord say,

00:04:31.990 --> 00:04:32.000
'It will

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.710
be a

00:04:34.710 --> 00:04:34.720
flow.'I

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:37.030
see the

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:39.670
eyes, ears,

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:41.590
toes, and what you have been

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:44.230
believing for from these great

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:46.150
silos,

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:48.950
for I am emptying them out.

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:53.110
I hear Him say, 'What

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:55.270
new do you need to hear? I

00:04:55.270 --> 00:04:55.280
have

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:58.790
reserved it for today,

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:02.230
for a great move of My presence will be

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:06.230
upon My people.

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:09.350
I will empty the reserves,

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:11.510
for there is no need for it here; this

00:05:11.510 --> 00:05:11.520
is

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:13.670
what I call, and it will draw

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:17.189
you near. For it is

00:05:24.479 --> 00:05:26.310
My goodness that will

00:05:26.310 --> 00:05:26.320
bring

00:05:26.320 --> 00:05:27.830
them to

00:05:27.830 --> 00:05:27.840
repentance.

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:31.749
My goodness will pass through. It will be My goodness and My mercy that you will

00:05:31.749 --> 00:05:31.759
see—something you did not

00:05:31.759 --> 00:05:34.150
earn and

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:37.029
did

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:42.390
not

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:47.350
deserve.'I

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:50.870
hear the sound of an abundance of rain,

00:05:50.880 --> 00:05:53.749
for it will be the glory. Unto Him be all

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:57.830
the glory. I

00:05:57.830 --> 00:05:57.840
am

00:05:57.840 --> 00:06:00.790
emptying My silos; they

00:06:00.790 --> 00:06:00.800
are

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:03.029
dumping them out. It will come

00:06:03.039 --> 00:06:05.909
in on the

00:06:05.909 --> 00:06:05.919
waves—a

00:06:05.919 --> 00:06:07.749
wave of

00:06:07.749 --> 00:06:07.759
glory.

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:10.390
I see

00:06:10.400 --> 00:06:14.390
black arms, white arms, brown arms,

00:06:14.390 --> 00:06:14.400
and

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:17.990
yellow arms. Creative miracles: blue

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:21.350
eyes, black eyes, brown eyes, and green

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:25.749
eyes. As you walk in My authority, there

00:06:25.749 --> 00:06:25.759
will be

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:29.590
healings of hearts, livers,

00:06:29.590 --> 00:06:29.600
and

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:32.469
intestines. I see brand new

00:06:32.479 --> 00:06:35.270
colons. You might have a

00:06:35.270 --> 00:06:35.280
colostomy bag,

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:37.430
but He

00:06:37.430 --> 00:06:37.440
is

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:39.670
going to restore back what the

00:06:39.670 --> 00:06:39.680
cankerworm

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:42.629
ate. He said, 'There will

00:06:42.639 --> 00:06:46.870
be no sick among

00:06:46.870 --> 00:06:46.880
you.'Just

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:49.990
like the children of Israel,

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:53.110
they left with no sickness

00:06:53.110 --> 00:06:53.120
or

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.830
disease. You will walk in the

00:06:55.840 --> 00:06:59.510
same; it will be a type and shadow.

00:06:59.510 --> 00:06:59.520
This

00:06:59.520 --> 00:07:02.150
is

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:05.029
an outpouring over Africa,

00:07:05.039 --> 00:07:08.870
South America, and

00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:08.880
America.

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:11.510
He says, 'America,

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:15.749
get out of the thinking of the

00:07:15.749 --> 00:07:15.759
natural.'If

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:20.150
you resist

00:07:20.150 --> 00:07:20.160
this—I

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:23.589
see America and

00:07:23.589 --> 00:07:23.599
Africa—it is

00:07:23.599 --> 00:07:26.309
happening like ripe

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:28.950
cherries off a tree

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:30.790
for the

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:32.629
people who would just believe. He says,

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:35.350
'But you come up to how you

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:38.309
think it should be.'America

00:07:38.309 --> 00:07:38.319
tries

00:07:38.319 --> 00:07:40.790
to block it

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:42.790
like with a

00:07:42.790 --> 00:07:42.800
dam

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:46.150
because of the traditions of man.

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:49.589
Get out of the natural thinking;

00:07:49.599 --> 00:07:52.870
come up higher with Me. Do not be a dam; be a river. Let the Holy Ghost flow like He can

00:07:52.870 --> 00:07:52.880
in Africa.

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:56.950
Let Him

00:07:56.960 --> 00:07:58.469
flow

00:08:06.879 --> 00:08:11.350
through America.

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:14.230
I see

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:17.670
the waves of

00:08:17.670 --> 00:08:17.680
glory.

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:20.469
Before a wave is able to

00:08:20.479 --> 00:08:22.710
come back, another wave will come on top

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:26.790
of it, for I am emptying My silos.

00:08:26.800 --> 00:08:29.110
This is the great finale He has

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.550
for us—the greatest finale of all.

00:08:32.560 --> 00:08:35.750
His goodness will be displayed upon

00:08:37.599 --> 00:08:39.990
everyone.

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:46.870
His goodness and mercy will follow

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:49.829
all over you. I have the greatest

00:08:49.839 --> 00:08:53.269
treasures for you. Do

00:08:53.269 --> 00:08:53.279
not

00:08:53.279 --> 00:08:55.430
become accustomed to what He is about to

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:58.070
do, taking it for granted when you hear

00:08:58.080 --> 00:08:59.509
about someone else getting a blessing.

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:04.070
Everything is

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:07.350
precious that you will see.

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:16.470
This is what Kathryn

00:09:16.470 --> 00:09:16.480
Kuhlman

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:18.949
desired to see. I heard Him just say

00:09:18.959 --> 00:09:21.269
this is what Kathryn Kuhlman desired to

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:22.710
see, and she did not see the full

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:25.430
manifestation of it. She

00:09:25.430 --> 00:09:25.440
is

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:27.670
standing

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:29.030
in the great cloud of

00:09:29.040 --> 00:09:31.829
witnesses. She is watching,

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:37.430
wearing the same outfit she had on earth with the bell sleeves. She is looking out, anticipating what

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:39.990
she

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:53.910
is about

00:09:53.910 --> 00:09:53.920
to

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:56.630
see.

00:09:56.640 --> 00:09:59.269
Isn't it amazing

00:09:59.279 --> 00:10:01.590
the Lord allows me to

00:10:01.590 --> 00:10:01.600
see

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:03.590
the ones who have gone before

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.030
us? They

00:10:05.030 --> 00:10:05.040
are

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:08.070
anticipating this glorious outpouring.

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:10.630
Kim Clement was there,

00:10:10.640 --> 00:10:11.910
and now I see Kathryn

00:10:11.910 --> 00:10:11.920
Kuhlman

00:10:11.920 --> 00:10:13.269
looking over

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:15.590
a portal.

00:10:20.800 --> 00:10:22.790
There is

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:24.790
an edge with grass and Kathryn

00:10:24.790 --> 00:10:24.800
Kuhlman is

00:10:24.800 --> 00:10:25.910
sitting right there. There is a wall

00:10:25.910 --> 00:10:25.920
that

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:28.790
looks like a well,

00:10:28.800 --> 00:10:31.509
or

00:10:31.519 --> 00:10:33.670
like a TV

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:35.269
screen,

00:10:35.279 --> 00:10:38.630
but it is not. It is a well of water.

00:10:38.640 --> 00:10:41.670
I can see a

00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:44.630
well of water, and they come up and they

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:48.949
can see over into it. It's a round hole,

00:10:48.959 --> 00:10:52.150
a portal, showing glimpses of

00:10:52.160 --> 00:10:53.910
what's happening in certain parts of the

00:10:53.920 --> 00:10:56.470
earth, and they're able to see into it.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:11:00.230
It actually has

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:02.710
bricks that are built up around

00:11:02.710 --> 00:11:02.720
it;

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:05.269
it looks like a cobblestone well. Catherine

00:11:05.269 --> 00:11:05.279
is

00:11:05.279 --> 00:11:07.030
looking over this.

00:11:07.040 --> 00:11:08.710
There's green grass on this side, and

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:10.470
she's looking over into it. It's like

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:13.590
a picture show,

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:17.110
but if you touched it, you

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.790
could interrupt the water. You

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:19.829
know how when you see your

00:11:19.839 --> 00:11:22.870
reflection in the water

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:24.710
and if you touch it, it goes away

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:27.590
until the water's calm again? It's like

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:29.590
that. It's a well, and

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:32.550
you can see into it. I can see

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:36.630
her face looking into this.

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:39.750
She's looking over and watching,

00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:42.870
anticipating the greatest move of the

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:45.190
Spirit of God that we've ever seen.

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:49.030
They're all anticipating.

00:11:49.040 --> 00:11:52.630
The silos are being emptied.

00:11:54.480 --> 00:11:58.470
The angelic host

00:11:58.480 --> 00:12:01.350
are emptying the silos right now. The

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:02.870
Lord said, 'Why do I have need of them

00:12:02.880 --> 00:12:04.470
here?

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:06.550
I've saved them for

00:12:06.550 --> 00:12:06.560
today.'It's

00:12:06.560 --> 00:12:10.310
now. He saved them for this last show.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:12.550
This is the grand finale. When you get

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:15.350
up here, they'll be empty. You'll see.

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:19.269
Reach out by faith and receive. That's

00:12:19.279 --> 00:12:21.430
what I just heard him say. Reach out

00:12:21.440 --> 00:12:25.110
with simple faith as a child and

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:27.829
receive. Don't think like an adult;

00:12:27.839 --> 00:12:30.069
think like a child.

00:12:30.079 --> 00:12:33.910
He said, 'Come to me as a child.

00:12:33.920 --> 00:12:36.629
Reach out by faith and receive just like

00:12:36.639 --> 00:12:39.590
a child would receive.'That's what I

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:41.430
heard the Lord say. And I see these

00:12:41.440 --> 00:12:43.430
children; they're so easily able to

00:12:43.440 --> 00:12:45.509
receive it. They don't have any doubt.

00:12:45.519 --> 00:12:48.069
Doubt is taught because of life

00:12:48.079 --> 00:12:49.990
circumstances, but a child believes

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:52.870
without doubt. They just believe. 'We're

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:54.710
going to get that for you.''Okay,

00:12:54.710 --> 00:12:54.720
Dad.'They

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:57.829
just trust. He said, 'Come to me as

00:12:57.839 --> 00:13:00.230
the children would come to

00:13:00.230 --> 00:13:00.240
you.'Like

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:02.470
trust.

00:13:02.480 --> 00:13:04.470
Disappointment comes in because you let

00:13:04.470 --> 00:13:04.480
them

00:13:04.480 --> 00:13:06.150
down, but

00:13:06.160 --> 00:13:08.150
I'm telling you, come to God like

00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:10.710
this child. I see the wave. I hear

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:13.350
the wave. And it will

00:13:13.360 --> 00:13:15.430
come on the hill with the

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:17.030
greatest outpouring. This greatest

00:13:17.030 --> 00:13:17.040
well—I

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:19.590
see people coming to

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:22.230
Jesus.

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:25.269
Remember even with Jesus, he didn't

00:13:25.279 --> 00:13:27.750
heal the saved; he healed the

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.110
sinner.

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:31.750
It's the goodness of God that brings men

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:34.150
to repentance, and his goodness and

00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:37.110
mercy will flow over me.

00:13:39.200 --> 00:13:41.829
I see gold coins

00:13:43.920 --> 00:13:46.230
raining down.

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:49.110
This represents

